WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:56.796
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:56.796 --> 00:01:03.580
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:45.413
I wasn't going to do a video tonight; I was going to take the day off, but I felt in my spirit we could just talk over some things real quick and we'll pray.

00:01:56.360 --> 00:01:56.600
We saw a lot of progress in our prayers for the nations even from the last 48 hours when we did those back-to-back videos.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:24.320
I told you I believe with all my heart God has assembled the greatest prayer group of any generation for such a time as this with people like you.

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:39.360
He said, "Braden, I'm bringing my best," and I truly believe it, that the veterans and the newbies, the ones that are learning how to pray, I'm telling you, I really believe we're changing things.

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:45.469
And so, finding these weapons of mass destruction has been on my heart all day.

00:02:45.469 --> 00:02:52.120
I truly believe they're in the northeast, underneath this mountain.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:55.120
I keep seeing this mountain.

00:02:55.120 --> 00:03:01.720
And if you go back to what we were looking at yesterday, I'll give a little recap real quick.

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:06.560
I saw the man with the black hat hiding.

00:03:06.970 --> 00:03:11.400
I don't know; it sounds like they found him today.

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:13.711
I don't know if this is true.

00:03:13.711 --> 00:03:26.480
I'm getting a lot of fake news, so you don't know who is real and who is not, but some people say that he was injured and they took his leg.

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:35.813
Benny Johnson on his show tonight was saying that they believe that he was injured and they might have taken his leg off because of the injuries that he's sustained.

00:03:35.813 --> 00:03:47.440
I don't know if that's fake news or not, but as I continue to pray, I believe that the Lord is going to deal with this man, too.

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:50.519
Some people say he's worse than the last one.

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:54.080
There's so much news.

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:59.189
There's so much stuff coming in that I said, "What do you believe and what do you not believe?

00:03:59.377 --> 00:04:03.920
" You have to really just filter it and go with what you're praying over.

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:19.703
President Trump declaring that he believes the war is over; the economy, like I told you—Israel hit, from what I understand, every oil and gas plant in Iran.

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:33.000
And if that is true, if they've hit every single one of them, this is exactly what the Lord showed us in our prayer time back in June of last year.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:46.040
And he told us that Israel would strike all the oil wells and the oil refineries, and there would be war on the Strait of Hormuz.

00:04:52.434 --> 00:04:58.480
We see that happening.

00:04:59.760 --> 00:05:19.840
Oil went up to $120 a barrel today as crude was skyrocketing because of the news of Israel, and then Iran hit one of Israel's main oil plants and their gas plants where they make diesel and everything else.

00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:24.440
They hit their largest plant, from what I understood last night.

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:30.960
So, they struck their oil wells; they blew up all of theirs.

00:05:31.290 --> 00:05:35.057
When that happened, oil shot up to $120 a barrel.

00:05:35.057 --> 00:05:38.307
Now, President Trump came on and said, "The war is over.

00:05:38.307 --> 00:05:40.394
It looks like we're about over.

00:05:40.394 --> 00:06:07.300
" Then oil started going back down when he and Putin said they were coming to an agreement on lifting the sanctions off of the oil for trade with Russia, which I know President Trump probably is trying to help our economy and he doesn't want people mad at him because midterms are coming.

00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:19.480
If you have gas lines and $10-a-gallon gas, you're going to have a lot of upset Americans.

00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:45.745
As we're praying into these things and seeing it, I believe the visions that the Lord shows me are so prayer changes things—that we don't have the gas lines, that we don't have massive gas prices go above $10 a gallon, and the anti-Semitism and all the things that the Lord has shown me.

00:06:45.745 --> 00:06:49.840
I know because part of the vision has already come true.

00:06:52.285 --> 00:07:00.560
The war with Iran, the striking of all the oil wells—that part of the vision has happened, manifested completely.

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:07.640
The gas lines and oil going to $200 a barrel—this is the part where it split.

00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:12.040
And so far it only went to $120.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:14.040
No gas lines.

00:07:14.512 --> 00:07:18.556
It's interesting to me, the things that I see and we're praying over.

00:07:21.971 --> 00:07:27.480
Between all channels, we had probably 150,000 people pray over that last night.

00:07:32.234 --> 00:07:40.040
I'm not quite to 200,000, but just a little under with all seven channels.

00:07:40.252 --> 00:07:42.360
I give all the glory to God.

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:45.316
There's so many of you that come out and pray like that.

00:07:46.862 --> 00:07:48.187
I know the power of prayer.

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:51.907
If you get one of us to pray, good; two agreeing touching anything...

00:07:51.907 --> 00:07:58.200
just think about almost 200,000 people praying for up to two or three hours.

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:04.440
That's amazing.

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:08.556
I believe that we're changing things.

00:08:10.533 --> 00:08:13.600
I pray we don't see gas go up to $10 a gallon.

00:08:18.373 --> 00:08:24.222
That would be terrible and it would affect our economy greatly.

00:08:24.644 --> 00:08:28.422
Half of it is in the news, half of it's not.

00:08:28.587 --> 00:08:30.380
The power of prayer there.

00:08:30.380 --> 00:08:39.400
Number two, the Lord showed us yesterday, I believe, one weapon.

00:08:39.400 --> 00:08:48.760
And as I was in the spirit again, I could hear that new leader talking to a scientist.

00:08:48.760 --> 00:08:51.400
"Does it work?

00:08:51.400 --> 00:08:53.320
" I could hear him in English.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:55.440
"Does it work?

00:08:55.440 --> 00:09:03.696
" The scientist, in a white outfit, said, "It has not been tested yet, but we believe we have successfully built the bomb.

00:09:08.955 --> 00:09:20.360
" It was ready to put on a rocket; it looked as long as a school bus, like a massive city bus.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:47.720
That's how big this thing was—a fat, round-looking rocket.

00:09:47.937 --> 00:09:51.126
They were pointing at this rocket saying that could be the payload.

00:09:52.126 --> 00:09:56.040
They were discussing this one thing.

00:09:56.040 --> 00:10:01.400
They only had one, but it was not tested.

00:10:01.604 --> 00:10:06.670
They said, "So, we don't know if it will work, but we all believe that it will.

00:10:07.987 --> 00:10:16.870
We only have one.

00:10:16.880 --> 00:10:20.760
" And I believe that was a nuclear something.

00:10:20.760 --> 00:10:28.480
If you go back to what the Lord said: Hiroshima.

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:30.180
Go back to that.

00:10:30.180 --> 00:10:32.525
That was an atom bomb.

00:10:35.611 --> 00:10:48.000
It wasn't like what we have now, these great big ones, but it was still something very significant that hit Japan in World War II.

00:10:54.760 --> 00:11:04.080
The Lord told us this, but as I was hearing this scientist talking to the man with the black hat, black turban, they kept talking back and forth: "What do we have at our disposal?

00:11:39.129 --> 00:11:39.511
What bigger artillery do we have underground?

00:11:39.511 --> 00:11:46.080
" They were discussing things, getting ready for a surprise attack against Israel with biological weapons.

00:11:56.256 --> 00:11:56.520
I saw biological weapons.

00:12:19.830 --> 00:12:20.055
I saw containers that were underneath the ground.

00:12:21.205 --> 00:12:21.760
They were separated out by Agent Orange.

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:37.044
And there were three different kind of things.

00:12:39.267 --> 00:12:43.949
The first one looked like a mustard-yellow substance because the Lord highlighted it with a color.

00:12:43.949 --> 00:12:53.020
It was in a black drum, but in the spirit I could see a color on it.

00:12:57.350 --> 00:12:57.560
The next one was red.

00:12:57.560 --> 00:13:03.080
They only had about six or seven barrels stacked up three high.

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:12.360
The others were over here and I could see them being stored, but there was a lot of it—50 or 60 barrels or more.

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:17.990
This one looked red, and I saw on it the letter Y.

00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:29.120
I'm still praying about it, but it was some kind of biological weapon, chemical warfare.

00:13:34.100 --> 00:13:34.320
It was right next to it.

00:13:52.911 --> 00:13:53.169
That was something in the spirit realm.

00:13:53.169 --> 00:14:06.912
When I was looking at it, there was something that looked like another kind of object, but I couldn't focus on it.

00:14:15.400 --> 00:14:21.480
The visions come very fast and whenever I'm looking, so many things are coming at me.

00:14:24.590 --> 00:14:35.080
I don't take the time, because I'm on a live stream, to pause it and try to look into it.

00:14:35.640 --> 00:14:37.587
That's the trouble with being live.

00:14:39.200 --> 00:15:00.900
If it were in my private time, I would spend all day on that because I pray over it, and what I've learned to do is freeze-frame it in the spirit and just pray specifically over those biological weapons for hours and be able to focus in and look around them.

00:15:12.040 --> 00:15:13.384
It is all by the Spirit of God, all to the glory of God.

00:15:21.738 --> 00:15:22.185
I didn't do that last night, though I wish I would have now.

00:15:28.640 --> 00:15:28.885
I saw the missiles.

00:15:28.885 --> 00:15:30.355
They were painted black.

00:15:53.657 --> 00:15:54.046
Some were big, some were small.

00:15:59.314 --> 00:16:08.264
I believe with all my heart this is under a mountain in the northeast area of Iran, closer to Afghanistan.

00:16:08.264 --> 00:16:15.069
Turkmenistan is northeast up here, and this is Afghanistan.

00:16:15.069 --> 00:16:20.840
If I can see the map?

00:16:20.840 --> 00:16:25.575
I'm talking about the north-northeast area.

00:16:25.575 --> 00:16:28.537
So it had to be Turkmenistan.

00:16:34.265 --> 00:16:34.651
I see Iran and the mountains.

00:16:35.036 --> 00:16:41.440
In this vision, I saw mountains and I kept seeing northeast.

00:16:57.330 --> 00:16:57.940
It was underneath these mountains—great facilities.

00:17:14.629 --> 00:17:22.515
It doesn't matter anymore; I'm moving on.

00:17:22.515 --> 00:17:24.568
We have to do this quickly.

00:17:24.568 --> 00:17:26.786
I need your help.

00:17:42.458 --> 00:17:42.640
What else?

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:44.740
I see, lower shows.

00:17:44.740 --> 00:17:47.326
You saw the new weapon?

00:17:47.326 --> 00:17:48.349
Thank you.

00:17:48.349 --> 00:17:52.011
Then I saw America's new weaponry.

00:18:02.456 --> 00:18:03.088
The Lord said that nobody else in the world, other than Israel, has some things that we've seen.

00:18:03.088 --> 00:18:35.410
Remember that the Lord said, 'I have granted the United States supernatural wisdom to get this weaponry to liberate and set free the nations of the world that are suppressed and oppressed from religious freedom: Venezuela, Cuba, North Korea, Iran, Pakistan, and these other nations.

00:18:35.410 --> 00:18:43.310
' I saw in the vision something that was stronger than nuclear, but it was water-based.

00:18:52.635 --> 00:18:52.840
A splitting of water that was a sustainable energy that never loses its power.

00:18:52.840 --> 00:18:56.600
It is better than fossil fuels; it is better than nuclear.

00:18:56.600 --> 00:18:59.440
This was a new type of energy, but it was blue.

00:18:59.440 --> 00:19:11.533
As it was glowing, I saw Elon Musk putting it on things to fly around and on rocket ships and Air Force planes so that you don't have to refuel them.

00:19:11.533 --> 00:19:16.920
They would be able to sustain energy indefinitely, like an F-16.

00:19:22.320 --> 00:19:31.860
I don't know what they have now, but planes that were fighter jets had turbines in the back with blue energy that was continually bubbling.

00:19:31.860 --> 00:19:42.330
It was cleaner energy than fossil fuels ever thought about being, but it was being harnessed only by the military for their special interests.

00:19:51.431 --> 00:19:51.622
It wasn't commercial; it wasn't used in a Ford F-150.

00:20:09.260 --> 00:20:10.440
It was used in spacecraft.

00:20:16.675 --> 00:20:17.284
I thought that was interesting.

00:20:31.417 --> 00:20:41.680
I saw secret weapons that we are about to use that will make the earth shock in awe at the technological advancements we have achieved only by the hand of God.

00:20:47.377 --> 00:20:52.920
The Lord said, 'I have restrained it where China has not been able to touch this.

00:20:52.920 --> 00:21:00.235
' I have held this back so that China...

00:21:00.235 --> 00:21:06.907
you know, it's like you have a block.

00:21:06.907 --> 00:21:20.204
You're able to see certain things because you're using part of your brain you never knew you had.

00:21:20.204 --> 00:21:28.253
Some people have really high IQs and some folks don't.

00:21:28.253 --> 00:21:35.440
You wonder how it is so clear to some and not for others.

00:21:35.440 --> 00:21:57.747
Their minds are different, but the Lord said, 'I put it on certain people to be able to achieve this technological advancement for the liberation and setting free of these nations.

00:21:57.747 --> 00:22:06.187
' In the days ahead, I will use this, but Trump must remain humble with this.

00:22:18.472 --> 00:22:18.856
It's not a dictatorship; it is a liberation.

00:22:40.510 --> 00:22:40.805
That makes sense where you don't come across like the Romans who would just wipe out anybody.

00:22:40.805 --> 00:22:47.900
We could go and pick a fight because we have the best stuff in the world.

00:22:48.240 --> 00:23:00.142
The Lord showed me that some of the technological advancements would be so overpowering that even Emmanuel Macron would freak out at the stuff we've never shown before.

00:23:00.142 --> 00:23:05.215
We have held it back and are about to release it.

00:23:05.215 --> 00:23:06.440
It will be concerning Cuba.

00:23:06.440 --> 00:23:32.093
I've told you I saw Marco Rubio helping liberate the people of Cuba, Venezuela, and Mexico in the days ahead—putting people in authority, helping establish the economy.

00:23:32.093 --> 00:23:43.480
I saw new resorts for vacation and economic growth out of Cuba with golf courses and things like that.

00:23:45.731 --> 00:23:52.150
A beautiful tourist industry is coming to Cuba in the days ahead with great hotels and facilities.

00:23:52.150 --> 00:24:04.608
Major American chains will go in there, buy up the land, and build resorts.

00:24:28.400 --> 00:24:28.920
I saw it coming.

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:53.360
I saw Cuban cigar facilities exploding and I saw them distributing their cigars and doing things with their tobacco products.

00:24:55.280 --> 00:25:03.857
I saw a new leader rise up who was not a tyrant.

00:25:03.857 --> 00:25:12.549
As I was praying into that last night, I saw gangs and bosses that would start to turn.

00:25:14.610 --> 00:25:21.760
I saw African American men that had blue uniforms on with berets and blue camouflage who were protecting the leader of Cuba.

00:25:27.340 --> 00:25:34.630
But then I saw a revolt in the nation because they wanted freedom for the first time in decades.

00:25:34.640 --> 00:25:50.027
They wanted prosperity and for their families to have a better life.

00:25:50.027 --> 00:25:53.080
It was coming.

00:25:53.080 --> 00:26:05.987
I saw a blessing increase coming to the Cuban people, same with Venezuela with our oil and all the other things.

00:26:05.987 --> 00:26:19.730
We prayed against the guerrilla warfare coming out of Brazil and Colombia to attack the oil wells.

00:26:19.730 --> 00:26:37.458
We've been praying to stop that because I saw drug lords blackmailing families, telling them if they don't fight against the American troops and stop this from happening, they will take their family out and torture them.

00:26:38.036 --> 00:26:38.613
It was bad.

00:26:38.613 --> 00:26:57.120
I saw young men who didn't want to fight but were coming against us because they knew the terrain to try to get the oil wells in Venezuela.

00:26:57.120 --> 00:27:06.960
Praying over the secret cells in our nation, I saw an underground communication that was not the internet.

00:27:14.463 --> 00:27:23.377
It was a way the Iranian leader would communicate to the cells of people in our nation by telephone, but it was a rotary phone.

00:27:23.377 --> 00:27:38.745
It wasn't like a cell phone; it was some kind of old communication that was not able to be tracked as easily because you're not looking for it.

00:27:38.745 --> 00:27:43.820
They're trying to outsmart the 'smart' with 'dumb' technology.

00:27:47.320 --> 00:27:47.820
The Lord said, 'Remember the carrier pigeons?

00:27:47.820 --> 00:27:49.307
Remember Morse code?

00:27:49.307 --> 00:28:00.150
Remember the Cherokee Indians talking in World War II?

00:28:00.160 --> 00:28:11.000
' He said they're trying to communicate in a way that is out of the ordinary.

00:28:22.800 --> 00:28:35.227
I saw a telephone to telephone, and as this line went across America, there were little cords that were stretched from them to rotary phones in each area, getting ready to give them the command to stir up these cells.

00:28:35.227 --> 00:28:44.960
In our nation, as I was praying last night, I saw our nuclear power plants.

00:28:45.120 --> 00:28:52.028
I saw Hoover Dam and other major dams for electricity and what we use.

00:28:52.028 --> 00:28:57.080
If that happened, it would be a very catastrophic, bad thing.

00:28:57.080 --> 00:29:15.600
Now, I don't know how much explosive it would take to take out a dam that size like Hoover Dam, but that would be something very significant and you surely would see that coming.

00:29:15.600 --> 00:29:22.360
The Lord kept showing me in the vision U-Haul trucks, like Timothy McVeigh using fertilizer.

00:29:22.713 --> 00:29:34.380
I saw these dams, the Las Vegas Strip, and these major cities, and I named every single one of them off last night.

00:29:46.280 --> 00:29:47.800
I said, from Boston, New York, Philadelphia, and Chicago, and I told you every single one that was popping up concerning hotels, concerning Trump Towers, and concerning key landmarks.

00:29:47.800 --> 00:29:59.027
As I saw each one of these cities had over a hundred men that were stationed there for some kind of event, but they were waiting on the phone call.

00:29:59.027 --> 00:30:11.108
Just like our military does not do anything outside of the commander-in-chief telling them to do it—take the shot or not—they don't go rogue; they don't just operate out of what they think.

00:30:11.108 --> 00:30:16.947
They're strategic orders because they are not terrorists.

00:30:16.947 --> 00:30:23.065
This is an invasion from another nation, and that's what the Lord showed me.

00:30:32.600 --> 00:30:32.760
He said, "You are not looking at terrorists; you're looking at an invasion because of the Biden administration.

00:30:32.760 --> 00:30:38.909
They let these people in without border security over those four years, and because of it, they have flooded your nation.

00:30:42.840 --> 00:30:50.535
" And he said, "There's other nations that are in your nation, China, with secret groups also, but the main group that you should be focused on praying for right now is the Iranians.

00:30:50.535 --> 00:30:52.320
They have infiltrated your nation.

00:30:53.400 --> 00:30:58.960
" I saw these men, and the Lord said, "Pray over your high schools, your college campuses.

00:30:58.960 --> 00:31:00.400
Plead the blood.

00:31:01.208 --> 00:31:05.470
" I told you to anoint your children with oil and pray over the churches.

00:31:15.520 --> 00:31:15.869
And the Lord said, "Watch the end of Ramadan.

00:31:15.869 --> 00:31:18.728
It is coming next week.

00:31:18.728 --> 00:31:44.600
Praying over Ramadan, the end of it going into our holy day; our holy week is Easter in two weeks, the first part of April.

00:31:44.600 --> 00:32:00.617
" Praying over our churches and our gatherings because the largest services we have—I believe it's April 5th—yeah, praying over Easter on April 5th, small and large churches.

00:32:14.830 --> 00:32:15.200
Praying over our services and, Lord, praying clear into the celebrations for the 250th anniversary.

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:39.520
You know, ladies and gentlemen, I know some of the things I say are heavy, but I know that the power of prayer changes things.

00:32:43.996 --> 00:32:56.836
And I know that he has called us to the kingdom for such a time as this: to pray for Trump, to pray for his family, and to pray for his sons, Eric and Don Jr.

00:33:10.400 --> 00:33:11.260
, specifically the most.

00:33:28.850 --> 00:33:29.620
Not saying that Tiffany, Ivanka, and Barron are not important; these are the ones that are highlighted to me to pray over: the two older sons.

00:33:40.080 --> 00:33:40.280
The Lord said specifically Don Jr.

00:33:46.038 --> 00:33:46.836
the most.

00:33:47.635 --> 00:33:53.867
I saw him the most in the visions and I continue to do so.

00:33:53.867 --> 00:34:03.080
And we will continue to pray for his family and his daughter, Kai, that no weapon formed against them will prosper.

00:34:03.080 --> 00:34:17.406
Praying over President Trump that he will finish his term, that the blood of Jesus Christ covers him, and that he will have a clarity of thought.

00:34:22.360 --> 00:34:27.760
That devil I saw in his office that looked like a blackbird kept reaching down and pecking at his head.

00:34:49.600 --> 00:34:50.080
And the Lord said, "That is a spirit messing with him.

00:34:50.080 --> 00:35:10.507
" I saw all the spirit and it was cloaked; it was hidden, and a lot of people couldn't see; you could only see it by the spirit of God.

00:35:21.656 --> 00:35:22.388
I saw it, and it kept like a woodpecker picking at his mind trying to make him nest, like Joe Biden yielded himself to that demonic spirit.

00:35:22.388 --> 00:35:37.680
I saw that snake crawl up by his feet and wrap around his whole body and start talking in his ear.

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:47.070
It was a black serpent that looked like a constrictor.

00:35:58.747 --> 00:35:58.911
It was wrapped around his head and it started talking in his ear, and he was listening to a demonic spirit.

00:35:58.911 --> 00:36:07.225
I saw it as he was staring out the window.

00:36:07.225 --> 00:36:20.460
There's a lot of people that saw that video, and a lot of people didn't; that's clear back when we first started.

00:36:22.400 --> 00:36:24.000
And the Lord said, "You must pray.

00:36:25.650 --> 00:36:31.220
" And we pray for Joe Biden just like we pray for President Trump.

00:36:35.760 --> 00:36:40.820
I have to say—no, I refrain that—I pray for Trump a lot more than I ever pray for Biden.

00:36:45.776 --> 00:36:46.052
I probably should have prayed for Biden more; I didn't.

00:36:52.840 --> 00:36:53.107
It was hard for me because I did not like that man.

00:36:53.107 --> 00:37:04.210
But I prayed for him—it wasn't always easy—and I still prayed for Kamala Harris and I prayed for our nation, but it wasn't always easy.

00:37:04.210 --> 00:37:13.040
But I pray for Trump all the time, and I will continue to do so.

00:37:13.040 --> 00:37:22.871
But I saw again: Rubio has slain his tens of thousands and Saul has slain his thousands.

00:37:35.890 --> 00:37:47.310
